d0/Bob-heart-ball.jpg\" alt=\"American Heart Association Heart Ball\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span><br />\n&nbsp;<br />\nBob and Peggy Wills chaired the live auction of the American Heart Association’s Heart Ball in San Antonio this past weekend. The Wills, as well as The PM Group, were proud supporters of this event that raises funds for the important work the American Heart Association does in the San Antonio community and nationwide. This year, the SA Heart Ball raised $663,645!<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<strong>About The PM Group:</strong> The PM Group was founded in 1988. Over the past 29 years, the agency has continued to grow and is currently listed as San Antonio’s Largest Advertising Agency by the San Antonio Business Journal. The PM Group’s client roster spans various industries including automotive, CPG, entertainment and sports marketing, legal, business services, non-profit, real estate and fitness. In addition, the agency hosts an annual Charity Gala that to date raised over $1 million for local San Antonio area non-profit organizations.</p>\n","title":"Bob and Peggy Wills Help American Heart Association Raise Over $660K","seo":{"breadcrumbs":[{"text":"Bob and Peggy Wills Help American Heart Association Raise Over $660K","url":"/bob-and-peggy-wills-help-american-heart-association-raise-over-660k/"}],"title":"CEO Assists American Heart Association Raise $660K | PMG","metaDesc":"Bob and Peggy Wills, as well as The PM Group, were proud supporters of the American Heart Association's Heart Ball in San Antonio raising over $660,000!","focuskw":"american heart association","metaKeywords":"","metaRobotsNoindex":"noindex","metaRobotsNofollow":"follow","opengraphTitle":"CEO Assists American Heart Association Raise $660K | PMG","opengraphDescription":"Bob and Peggy Wills, as well as The PM Group, were proud supporters of the American Heart Association's He